<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<title>JSP AJAX 실시간 회원제 채팅 서비스</title>	
      	<!-- jquery -->
		<script src="//code.jquery.com/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <!-- BootStrap -->
